d: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever relieves the hardship of a believer in this world, Allah will relieve his hardship on the Day of Resurrection. Whoever helps ease one in difficulty, Allah will make it easy for him in this world\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19188,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/19\/allah-covers-faults-brother\/","url_meta":{"origin":22480,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Faults: Allah covers faults of those who covered faults","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 19, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA servant does not cover the faults of another servant in the world but that Allah will cover his faults on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2590 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7286,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/29\/punish-trials-this-world\/","url_meta":{"origin":22480,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Trials: Punishment in this world as mercy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u